        <li><a href="#" class="block p-4 py-3">餐廳介紹</a></li>
        <li><a href="#booking" class="block p-4 py-3">立即訂位</a></li>
        <li><a href="#" class="block p-4 py-3">美食菜單</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="hidden md:flex">
      <ul class="hidden md:flex items-center">
        <li><a href="#" class="block p-4 py-3">餐廳介紹</a></li>
        <li><a href="#booking" class="block p-4 py-3">立即訂位</a></li>
        <li><a href="#" class="block p-4 py-3">美食菜單</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>
<div class="max-w-[85rem] px-4 py-4 md:px-6 xl:px-8 mt-1 mx-auto">
  <div class="aspect-w-16 aspect-h-7 flex">
    <%= image_tag "finedinning.webp", class:"top-10 w-full object-cover" %>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="my-6 mx-12 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
  <ul class="flex flex-wrap -mb-px text-sm font-medium text-center text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
    <li class="mr-2">
      <a href="#" name="booking" id="booking" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center p-4 border-b-2 border-transparent rounded-t-lg text-lg hover:text-blue-600 hover:border-blue-300 dark:hover:text-blue-300 group"><i class="fa-solid fa-calendar-days"> 我要訂位</i>
      </a>
    </li>
     <li class="mr-2">
      <a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center p-4 border-b-2 border-transparent rounded-t-lg text-lg hover:text-blue-600 hover:border-blue-300 dark:hover:text-blue-300 group"><i class="fa-solid fa-motorcycle"> 我要訂餐</i>
      </a>
    </li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div class="my-6 mx-12 ">
  <h1 class="m-4 text-3xl font-extrabold dark:text-white">貳樓 敦南店</h1>
  <p class="m-6"><i class="fa-solid fa-thumbs-up"> 4.0 <a href="" class="underline hover:text-blue-400">58 則評論</a></i></p>
  <p class="m-6">台北市敦化南路二段63巷14號</p>
  <p class="m-6"><i class="fa-solid fa-phone"></i> 02-2700-9855</p>
  <hr>
  <p class="m-6 text-lg text-gray-900 dark:text-white">貳樓餐廳為寵物友善餐廳，我們歡迎您攜帶寵物一起來用餐，煩請您可在訂位時先行告知會攜帶寵物，我們將可提前為您安排舒適位置，建議為了商場餐飲環境及顧客考量，攜帶寵物可置於寵物袋內(導盲犬除外)，謝謝您的體諒與配合！</p>
  <p class="m-6 text-lg text-gray-900 dark:text-white">此外，若希望鄰桌不安排寵物也可事先於訂位時備註讓我們為您安排合適的位置呦。</p>
  <hr>
</div>

<div class="my-6 mx-12" name="booking">
  <%= form_with(model: @reservations, data: { turbo: false }) do |f| %>
    <div class="my-6">
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between gap-4">
        <div class="w-full sm:w-1/4 sm:mb-0">
          <%= f.label :adult_num, '大人數',class:"text-sm text-gray-600" %>
          <%= f.number_field :adult_num, class:"h-9 w-full px-5 py-1 text-gray-700 bg-gray-200 rounded", min: 0 %>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full sm:w-1/4 sm:mb-0">
          <%= f.label :kid_num, '小孩數',class:"text-sm text-gray-600 mt-3 sm:mt-0" %>
          <%= f.number_field :kid_num, class:"h-9 w-full px-5 py-1 text-gray-700 bg-gray-200 rounded", min: 0 %>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full sm:w-1/2 sm:mb-0">
          <%= f.label :date, '用餐日期',class:"text-sm text-gray-600 mt-3 sm:mt-0" %>
          <%= f.date_field :kid_num, class:"h-9 w-full px-5 py-1 text-gray-700 bg-gray-200 rounded" %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  <% end %>
  <hr>
</div>
